  "detailed_description": "In the \"Classic of Mountains and Seas\", strange beasts have acquired the ability to jump. At this moment, you travel through to the world in the book, fly with a sword, and fight the strange beasts with all your might. In this process, you will obtain various bizarre \"swords\".<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756280/extras/74f53f6c71701382fe7c61a388f995c4.poster.avif?t=1750002560\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756280/extras/74f53f6c71701382fe7c61a388f995c4.webm?t=1750002560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756280/extras/74f53f6c71701382fe7c61a388f995c4.mp4?t=1750002560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each \"sword\" has its own unique characteristics. Equip these swords reasonably and engage in a desperate showdown with the strange beasts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756280/extras/642d6abcb9e9d1cd837bdc2f6438d4f8.poster.avif?t=1750002560\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756280/extras/642d6abcb9e9d1cd837bdc2f6438d4f8.webm?t=1750002560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756280/extras/642d6abcb9e9d1cd837bdc2f6438d4f8.mp4?t=1750002560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When you master the knack of matching \"swords\", playing will surely be extremely enjoyable.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756280/extras/35ec7922ba5a26ee3a4